lead_paragraph: Adam Eaton got a good jump on the liner down the right field line with the bases loaded and saw Ian Desmond break off first base. Eaton knew he had a chance for a double play even before he made the running catch.

headline.print_headline: White Sox Pull Off Triple Play in 5-0 Win Over Rangers
